{"tid":1883097,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★「檢疫令」單位 廁所為共用，有機會令病毒四散","createTime":"2020-02-16T16:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T06:09:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b8be7da1b16a765c9ba6b75c02e8d03342e27d1e","tid":1883097,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:58:25.000Z","msg":"正接受「檢疫令」的女住戶四處走動恐變「播毒炸彈」。本報記者在佐敦偉晴閣實地視察，違令女子所途經之處，至少有四個高危播毒點，包括單位對出走廊、升降機位置、大廈大堂以及最高危的廁所。由於廁所為樓層共用，加上屬於「踎廁」，有機會令病毒四散，有傳染病專家指家居檢疫的前提應有獨立起居以及如廁地方，上述家居隔離非常不理想，一旦接受隔離者屬帶病毒病人，或將病毒傳播開去。<br />\n<br />\n該住戶單位位於走廊末端，由於是商住大廈，該層內夾雜商舖及民居，另一走廊盡頭是女廁。雖然走廊僅短短數十米，但女住戶與女廁「一頭一尾」，每次去廁所時均需經過至少兩個單位門口、三個舖位、男廁、樓梯、兩部升降機及電錶房。最令人擔心是廁所屬樓層共用，一層只有一格男廁及一格女廁，廁格內屬踎廁，亦設有抽氣扇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200217/bkn-20200217000028079-0217_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200217%2Fbkn-20200217000028079-0217_00822_001.html&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ1HO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=f0192d8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200217/bkn-20200217000028079-0217_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1c744192af19fcd6a8dcd137ffe0a74e4a676a84","tid":1883097,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200217/photo/bkn-20200217000028079-0217_00822_001_02p.jpg?20200217004216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200217000028079-0217_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20200217004216&h=90d0d460&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"317d3bcd8b9939d3e89608c2a958d8752b3835d6","tid":1883097,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff4b34e6e2ad72cfbf7f4fe8962a1b29dff6938","tid":1883097,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T06:09:16.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}